:hugging_face:  Collaborations Workshop is happening THIS WEEK from 13-15 May in Stirling, Scotland! If you're around, please find members of the team and participate in our workshop!
:classical_building: Sign up to join our next Community Forum on 19 June at 15 - 16:30 London time - Sign up to join on Google forms
:phone: Our next onboarding call is scheduled for 28 May at 15:00 London time - Sign up to join on Google forms
 :email: Stay tuned for our April newsletter - which will be in your inboxes this week!
:mag_right: Do you have any outstanding issues/pull requests to highlight? Please add to our Github list, to be transferred for an issue: https://annuel2.framapad.org/p/ttw-github-update-list
Note - there are tons of community-related issues that we have flagged on our newsletter this month!
:white_check_mark: There are one ongoing meeting for working groups or teams this week.
:purple_heart: The Accessibility Working Group is meeting TODAY, 12 May at 3pm UK time. Join #accessibility for more information!
